## Finding a plumber you can trust

When a pipe leaks or a tap fails in Srinagar, you need someone reliable — fast. Here's what to look for:

### Check availability in your area

Not every provider covers every neighborhood. Panun Kaergar serves Lal Chowk, Rajbagh, Bemina, Nowgam, Rainawari, Soura, and more. Enter your address when booking to confirm coverage.

### Ask about the job upfront

Share photos or a clear description when you call, WhatsApp, or fill our booking form. This helps us assign the right plumber and give a realistic time estimate.

### Book your way

You don't need the app to get started. **Call us, WhatsApp us, fill the form at panunkaergar.com/book**, or download the app for self-service booking.

### After the visit

Pay as agreed (in-app or cash after service where available) and leave a review to help other Srinagar residents choose with confidence.
